com.spazedog.lib.rootfw3.extenders

Class BinaryExtender.Busybox

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spazedog.lib.rootfw3.extenders.BinaryExtender.Busybox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExtenderGroup
    Enclosing class:
    BinaryExtender

    public static class BinaryExtender.Busybox
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExtenderGroup
    This class is used to collect information about either a specific busybox binary, or the one found in the PATH environment variable.
    Note that this implements the ExtenderGroup interface, which means that it does not allow anything outside RootFW to create an instance of it. Use RootFW.busybox() or RootFW.busybox(String) to retrieve an instance.
